OL,6,FCiaran Fitzpatrick has been to see how
OL,7,Fthe initiative is working at a site
OL,8,Fnear Abingdon
OL,10,FMore than 80 thousand disposable vapes
OL,11,Fhave been recycled in Oxfordshire
OL,12,Fsince the launch of a scheme in
OL,13,FNovember last year.
OL,15,FResearch reveals 8.2 million vapes are
OL,16,Fbeing discarded or recycled improperly
OL,17,Facross the UK every week, a 37%
OL,18,Fincrease from last year, according to
OL,19,FMaterial Focus
