OL,4,Crecycled since launch of new scheme
OL,6,FIncorrect disposal of the items can
OL,7,Fcause safety risks, such as fires in
OL,8,Fbin lorries and waste facilities as
OL,9,Fwell as contaminating recycling
OL,10,Fstreams.
OL,12,FBut dealt with correctly, old vapes
OL,13,Fcan be given a whole new life.
OL,15,FIn Oxfordshire, a scheme was launched
OL,16,Flast year to enable people to recycle
OL,17,Fthem at seven centres, as well as curb
OL,18,Fside collection, supermarkets and
OL,19,Fhospitals.
