OL,3,CMore than 80,000 disposable vapes
OL,4,Crecycled since launch of new scheme
OL,6,FCouncil bosses say it's resulted in a
OL,7,Fdramatic increase in the amount of
OL,8,Fdisposable vapes being recycled.
OL,10,F"Last year we set a target for the
OL,11,Fproject to recycle two tonnes of
OL,12,Fvapes, which is in the region of
OL,13,F70,000 to 80,000 vapes," said Mark
OL,14,FWatson, Circular Economy Projects
OL,15,FOfficer, Oxfordshire County Council.
OL,17,F"We've actually recycled over that, so
OL,18,Fabout 2.5 tonnes have gone to a
OL,19,Frecycler and we've probably had about
OL,20,Fthree tonnes, so it has been a real
OL,21,Fsuccess."
