OL,6,F"We really thank the people who have
OL,7,Ftaken the time to do the right thing
OL,8,Fand put them in the right place."
OL,10,FAuthorities here benefitted from
OL,11,Faccess to 1.8 million pounds of
OL,12,Fnational funding from non profit
OL,13,FMaterial Focus.
OL,15,FThey campaign for ways to make it
OL,16,Feasier to recycle electronic goods.
OL,18,FA ban on disposable vapes will come
OL,19,Finto force next June. But there is a
OL,20,Ffear manufacturers may bend the rules.
