OL,6,F"Producers have started moving beyond
OL,7,Fwhat the definition for disposable
OL,8,Fwill be so we've got these "big puff"
OL,9,Fmodels that have come on the market,
OL,10,Fbut they're questionable whether
OL,11,Fthey're covered or not," said Material
OL,12,FFocus Executive Director, Scott Butler.
OL,14,F"Our concern is that you move from one
OL,15,Fissue to a different version of the
OL,16,Fissue."
OL,18,F"But we're here, we're now, eight-
OL,19,Fmillion a week, 13 a second and that
OL,20,Fneeds to be tackled."
